[13:25] [scene:talk]
VISUAL: 
AUDIO: 'then describe the type of scene that you\'re looking to build. So, you can see in this example here, we have our main character in this lab. Also got a shot of him here sat on a park bench. And an'

[13:37] [scene:talk]
VISUAL: 
