[14:03] [scene:talk]
VISUAL: 
AUDIO: 'you guys will agree that the voices that you hear in cartoon shows are just as important as everything that we\'ve already covered. It\'s crucial that the voices have a lot of character to them,'

[14:15] [scene:talk]
